foods.ingredients: Tomato Puree (Water, Tomato Paste), Cooked Enriched Lasagna (Water, Enriched Wheat Flour [Durum Wheat Semolina, Niacin, Ferrous Sulfate, Thiamine Mononitrate, Riboflavin, Folic Acid], Egg Whites), Seasoned Cooked Beef and Pork (Beef, Pork, Seasoning [Flavorings, Salt, Spice, Dextrose], Tomato Paste, Salt, Soybean Oil), Ricotta Cheese (Pasteurized Whey, Milk, Cream), Mozzarella Cheese (Part Skim Mozzarella Cheese [Pasteurized Milk, Cultures, Salt, Enzymes], Whey Protein Concentrate), Water, Contains 2% or less of: Parmesan and Romano (Made From Cow's Milk) Cheeses (Part-Skim Milk, Cheese Culture, Salt, Enzymes), Crushed Garlic (Garlic, Citric Acid), Carrots, Celery, Seasoning (Salt, Dextrose, Sugar, Spice, Spice Extractives [Including Paprika, Soy Lecithin], Disodium Inosinate, Disodium Guanylate), Sugar, Heavy Whipping Cream, Bread Crumbs (Wheat Flour, Sugar, Yeast, Soybean Oil, Salt), Spices, Onions, Modified Corn Starch, Salt, Dried Egg Whites. CONTAINS: WHEAT, EGG, MILK, SOY.
